            Radio-Canada, Compass, Ubisoft, EF Education First, Lightspeed, JBL,
            Harman Kardon, Audi, Jaguar, Ford, and Lincoln. <br /> My work helps people
            reach goals they set out to accomplish.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        id="contact-buttons"
        class="multi-col"
        style="--gtc: 1fr 1fr; --gap: 0.75em"
      >
        <a href="mailto:the.alexis.morin@gmail.com" class="aboutLink">
